      "sources": "Bilan Carbone Montpellier BS (45p, BL évolution)\nMBS Politique développement durable\nCP Bilan RSE MBS\nFondation MBS Rapport Moral 2021-22\nhttps://r.mbs-education.com/mbs-rse-accueil/\nhttps://r.mbs-education.com/mbs-rse-strategie-et-gouvernance/\nhttps://r.mbs-education.com/mbs-rse-formation-enseignements/\nhttps://r.mbs-education.com/mbs-rse-sante-bien-etre/\nhttps://r.mbs-education.com/mbs-rse-ouverture-sociale-inclusion/\nhttps://r.mbs-education.com/mbs-rse-recherche-engagee/\nhttps://r.mbs-education.com/mbs-rse-gestion-environnementale/\nhttps://www.mbs-education.com/fondation-mecenat/"
